"Residents are reminded to please exercise caution and to report any weather-related emergencies to the City’s 107 call centre by dialling 021 480 7700 from a cellphone or 107 from a landline.
"General service requests can be directed via the general call centre on 0860 103 089 or via the City’s website," the City said.

